node.text: Omggg this is so dope, thank you so much @courtneyakemp for giving me this opportunity! Never acted on a serious note a day in my life, and here you come turning a dream into reality 😢Sometimes it still feels surreal but thank you thank you thank you for believing in me 🥺❤️ Tune in @ MIDNIGHT , ALL NEW EPISODE PowerBook ll: Ghost 👻  Download the @starz app ✨
